    "After all, the human does not know why the correct answer is SWITCH.",
    "The obvious solution, given the need for genuinely helpful human-centric AI, is a class of artificial agents that can not only find solutions but also provide cogent, compelling, verified arguments certifying those solutions.",
    "If such a thing is provided in the present case, the human will be enlightened.",
    "As will be observed later in the study, this is what our artificial agents can do, even in cases where the percepts to these agents are \"clouded.\"",
    "The perception lacuna/challenge"
